with folkloric music.

00:15:23.080 --> 00:15:24.990
I mean, I'm a bit of
a control freak,

00:15:24.990 --> 00:15:27.950
so I just make sure
everything is in there.

00:15:27.950 --> 00:15:31.010
But you also want to
bulletproof the music.

00:15:31.010 --> 00:15:34.200
If you don't have such skilled
players as the H&amp;H musicians,

00:15:34.200 --> 00:15:36.810
