that need everything spelled

00:15:36.810 --> 00:15:39.410
out so then they can emote
and feel comfortable.

00:15:39.410 --> 00:15:43.180 position:56%
That's another reason why, if you're
making folkloric allusions, you try

00:15:43.180 --> 00:15:48.610
